\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]I'm telling you, even if I delete it, you won't
believe me...

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]...In the first place, it's just a matter of Minato-

know?

\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Guh... If you really deleted it, then it's fine... Well,
not really, but...

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]We won't speak a word about what happened inside the
mansion, and we won't leave any records either.
It's written in the contract, right?

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]After finishing the lesson and leaving the mansion, we
will just return to being a director and actors.
But well, that's only if Neon-chan wishes for it
at that time...

\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]...? A-anyway, today's lesson is over...? I'll go back
to my room...
\n<Udo>\F[\V[4]]Ah... wait a moment.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[4]]You don't have to wear a bra starting from tomorrow,
okay? Since you'll end up taking it off anyway,
it's just a hassle to put it on and take it off,
right?
\n<Minato>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]...Huh? What are you talking about...

\n<Udo>\FF[\V[2]]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Well, I'll leave that judgment up to you. Well then,
good work today♪
